class:: PifEqual
summary:: Embed values in a list if another ListPattern is equal to something.
related:: Classes/Pser
categories:: Streams-Patterns-Events>Patterns

description::

Simplified version of Pif(Pbinop(...), true, false).

Examples::

code::
(
Pbind(
  \a, Pseq([1,2,1,2,1,2], inf),
  \b, PifEqual(\a, 2, 3, 0),
)
)
::

